1
00:00:01,830 --> 00:00:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please go out with me!</font>

2
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:16,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, um... this is all kind of sudden for me.</font>

3
00:00:16,740 --> 00:00:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you give me some time to think?</font>

4
00:00:28,250 --> 00:00:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you just turn her down?</font>

5
00:00:30,520 --> 00:00:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is between me and Komari-chan. 
It isn't up to you.</font>

6
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure. We've never been more
 than childhood friends, anyway.</font>

7
00:00:47,730 --> 00:00:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing but childhood friends, right?!</font>

8
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just want to forget all this 
and light some black snakes.</i></font>

9
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From what the president said, 
it sounds like Komari might have a chance.</i></font>

10
00:02:34,570 --> 00:02:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never thought Tsukinoki-senpai 
might end up as a losing heroine.</i></font>

11
00:02:37,670 --> 00:02:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

12
00:02:39,970 --> 00:02:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you in here this whole time?</font>

13
00:02:41,860 --> 00:02:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't decide which one to go after.</font>

14
00:02:44,850 --> 00:02:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nukumizu...</font>

15
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I ask your advice?</font>

16
00:02:49,940 --> 00:02:51,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't believe this guy.</i></font>

17
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's basically like asking a worm
how to defeat a goldfish!</i></font>

18
00:02:57,630 --> 00:03:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I confessed to Koto once, 
but she turned me down.</font>

19
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:01,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

20
00:03:01,700 --> 00:03:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you serious? This must've been 
when you were, like, four or five, right?</font>

21
00:03:06,230 --> 00:03:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you say that? 
It was last Christmas.</font>

22
00:03:09,070 --> 00:03:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's kind of recent.</i></font>

23
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did she act like that after 
she'd already turned me down?</font>

24
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't make any sense.</font>

25
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Judging by how she reacted, 
there might be some misunderstanding.</font>

26
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First of all, you should go back 
and have a good talk with her.</font>

27
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you...</font>

28
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:31,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you actually really
 experienced in love?</font>

29
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why would you think that?</i></font>

30
00:03:38,570 --> 00:03:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Try swallowing first.</i></font>

31
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsukinoki-senpai took her things and left!</font>

32
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's she gonna go this late?</font>

33
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no idea.</font>

34
00:03:58,260 --> 00:03:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Koto.</font>

35
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you turned me down 
when I asked you out last Christmas.</font>

36
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:12,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Turned you down? Me?</font>

37
00:04:12,050 --> 00:04:17,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know. By that tree at the station. 
You said, "Yeah, in your dreams."</font>

38
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you said, "If you can't find someone to 
marry you, I guess I could fill in, so don't worry."</font>

39
00:04:22,150 --> 00:04:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that when?</font>

40
00:04:23,550 --> 00:04:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's what the president meant by a 
"confession"? That's worse that I imagined!</i></font>

41
00:04:28,450 --> 00:04:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On Christmas? Is that how you ask 
someone out on Christmas? In high school?</font>

42
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you completely brain dead?!</font>

43
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been waiting...</font>

44
00:04:41,810 --> 00:04:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All this time, I've been waiting for you.</font>

45
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Waiting and waiting.</font>

46
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Koto, I'm sorry.</font>

47
00:04:51,590 --> 00:04:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Yanami-san.</font>

48
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:56,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? But it's just starting to get good.</font>

49
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. Nukumizu-kun?</font>

50
00:05:02,530 --> 00:05:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you—</font>

51
00:05:03,140 --> 00:05:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We gotta go.</font>

52
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

53
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to give them some space.</font>

54
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What is it?</font>

55
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, uh, my hand?</font>

56
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you ever gonna let go of it?</font>

57
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, sorry! I-I-I didn't mean anything by it.</font>

58
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really sorry.</font>

59
00:05:24,850 --> 00:05:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to apologize <i>that</i> much.</font>

60
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this, Nukumizu-kun? 
Do you have something to confess to me?</font>

61
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, I don't.</font>

62
00:05:36,970 --> 00:05:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine with me. Go right ahead. 
I'll turn you down, though.</font>

63
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just said I don't!</font>

64
00:05:46,010 --> 00:05:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Nuk-kun, what are you doing out here?</font>

65
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are <i>you</i> doing, Yakishio?</font>

66
00:05:51,530 --> 00:05:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking for stag beetles.</font>

67
00:05:53,490 --> 00:05:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to give one to 
Komari-chan to cheer her up.</font>

68
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What makes you think a 
beetle will cheer her up?</i></font>

69
00:05:59,230 --> 00:06:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Check this one out. It's huge!</font>

70
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's in your hands now, Nuk-kun.</font>

71
00:06:07,230 --> 00:06:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I just talked to the president.</font>

72
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-He said no. Formally turned me down.</font>

73
00:06:16,850 --> 00:06:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did, huh? He actually 
gave you a straight answer?</font>

74
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Nukumizu, I bet you would've 
chickened out and made me wait.</font>

75
00:06:27,970 --> 00:06:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you guess?</font>

76
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You really are a jerk.</font>

77
00:06:34,990 --> 00:06:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The president actually thought about it.</font>

78
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He seriously considered
g-going out with me.</font>

79
00:06:46,790 --> 00:06:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For just a second, 
I had Tsukinoki-senpai beat.</font>

80
00:06:53,590 --> 00:06:57,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna cry. C-Can you leave me alone?</font>

81
00:06:58,930 --> 00:06:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please?</font>

82
00:07:06,210 --> 00:07:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Until recently, I'd never 
even talked to these people.</i></font>

83
00:07:10,230 --> 00:07:14,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now that we're here together, 
I'm getting caught up in all their drama.</i></font>

84
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's gonna happen after camp ends?</i></font>

85
00:07:21,130 --> 00:07:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll try writing something.</font>

86
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="12"><font color="#3e81ca">Become a
 Literary Icon</font></font></b></font></font>

87
00:07:26,970 --> 00:07:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, I'm submitting the first parts.</font>

88
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Komari-chan, is yours good like this?</font>

89
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, with that title. 
I don't want to split it up.</font>

90
00:07:36,450 --> 00:07:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want people to read part one like this.</font>

91
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:44,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good idea. That way, people 
can see the quality of your writing.</font>

92
00:07:46,250 --> 00:07:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, upload complete.</font>

93
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-President, I don't really know
 how to use the Lit Icon site,</font>

94
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I hope you'll keep showing me how.</font>

95
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. No problem.</font>

96
00:08:05,930 --> 00:08:13,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Senpai, I-I just uploaded my story,
 so please take a look.</font>

97
00:08:13,650 --> 00:08:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. I'll leave a comment.</font>

98
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

99
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And please keep coming to the club. 
I-It'd be lonely without you.</font>

100
00:08:29,110 --> 00:08:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Oh, gosh. Sorry, I don't mean to... Huh?</font>

101
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Senpai, you d-don't have 
to worry about me. So...</font>

102
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't cry. It's okay.</font>

103
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

104
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, did you see that yesterday?</font>

105
00:08:57,470 --> 00:08:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did, I did!</font>

106
00:08:58,310 --> 00:09:00,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Nuk-kun!</font>

107
00:09:01,090 --> 00:09:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Good morning.</font>

108
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a draft for the literature club.</font>

109
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this? A picture diary?</font>

110
00:09:07,100 --> 00:09:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Think you could upload 
it to that site for me?</font>

111
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:13,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, is that supposed to be me?</i></font>

112
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you upload yours, Nuk-kun?</font>

113
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, yeah. Just the beginning, though.</font>

114
00:09:21,450 --> 00:09:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey, you've already got comments!</font>

115
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, please upload mine 
when you get a chance.</font>

116
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, sure.</font>

117
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#c0c4c8">AM</font></font>

118
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="14"><font color="#353635">Halfwit on Love St.</font></font></font>

119
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="10"><b><font color="#c0c4c8">Save</font></b></font></font>

120
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><b><font color="#353635">Confirm
Settings</font></b></font></font>

121
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="14"><font color="#222322">My childhood friend, Sakura Misuzu, was wearing the uniform of Harukita
High School. I sneaked up on her to make fun of her, but she teased me first.</font></font></font>

122
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you hear? Yanami's been 
hanging around a new guy recently.</font>

123
00:09:50,190 --> 00:09:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

124
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who?</font>

125
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, that guy from our class. Um...</font>

126
00:09:56,650 --> 00:09:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nukumizu?</font>

127
00:09:58,230 --> 00:10:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the name rings a bell.</font>

128
00:09:58,610 --> 00:10:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="14"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#64715b">School Council 
Announcements</font></b></font></font></font>

129
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Yanami's pretty popular, right?</font>

130
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't she out of his league?</font>

131
00:10:05,330 --> 00:10:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For sure.</font>

132
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:09,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yanami's got bad taste.</font>

133
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

134
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:12,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't even know what he looks like, though.</font>

135
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what are they to each other, anyway?</font>

136
00:10:17,530 --> 00:10:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows?</font>

137
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I don't really get Yanami, either.</font>

138
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No kidding.</font>

139
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

140
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was pretty rude, Nukumizu-kun.</font>

141
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

142
00:10:49,210 --> 00:10:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You totally ignored me.</font>

143
00:10:50,730 --> 00:10:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I wasn't trying to.</font>

144
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. I guess that's okay, then.</font>

145
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cucumber and, uh, what's this? Moromi miso?</font>

146
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. What's it worth to you?</font>

147
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:09,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter?</font>

148
00:11:17,290 --> 00:11:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's worth 2,867 yen.</font>

149
00:11:19,530 --> 00:11:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! That's a new record...</font>

150
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Isn't that about the same
 as the remaining balance?</font>

151
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:32,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like I've been taking advantage 
of you this whole time, Yanami-san.</font>

152
00:11:32,830 --> 00:11:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think that's right. 
The bentos were really good, though.</font>

153
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for everything.</font>

154
00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This did all start because I didn't have 
enough money, but I'm enjoying it now.</font>

155
00:11:49,810 --> 00:11:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to call it off just like that.</font>

156
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People have been spreading rumors 
about us eating lunch together.</font>

157
00:11:58,280 --> 00:12:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want that, do you? 
People thinking that we might be—</font>

158
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen. I don't know 
where you're going with this.</font>

159
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I do something to hurt your feelings?</font>

160
00:12:08,410 --> 00:12:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

161
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you didn't.</font>

162
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I just don't like it.</font>

163
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want people spreading 
rumors like that about us.</font>

164
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, fine.</font>

165
00:12:28,140 --> 00:12:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's fine with me. 
I won't talk to you anymore.</font>

166
00:12:32,730 --> 00:12:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for everything. 
It was kind of fun. Bye.</font>

167
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem sorta out of it.</font>

168
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to worry. I'm always out of it.</font>

169
00:12:56,190 --> 00:13:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Or maybe you have someone on your mind?</font>

