00:15:30,210 --> 00:15:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not like that!</font>

215
00:15:31,930 --> 00:15:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes me so happy, man.</font>

216
