218
00:15:38,670 --> 00:15:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please take good care of her—</font>

219
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got it all wrong!</font>

220
00:15:44,250 --> 00:15:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know Yanami-san always 
liked you, right, Hakamada?</font>

221
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess...</font>

222
00:15:50,640 --> 00:15:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yanami-san and I aren't like that at all!</font>

223
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's still totally into you!</font>

224
00:15:56,220 --> 00:15:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, what are we all talking about, I wonder?</font>

