anything during vacation?</font>

328
00:19:51,320 --> 00:19:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Tsukinoki-senpai did say she 
wanted to do something together.</font>

329
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome! It's summer, so let's go hunt beetles!</font>

330
00:19:59,070 --> 00:20:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The training camp was fun, wasn't it?</font>

331
00:20:01,690 --> 00:20:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I guess so.</font>

332
00:20:05,430 --> 00:20:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? What is it?</font>

333
00:20:07,140 --> 00:20:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, uh, well...</font>

334
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tell you later.</font>

335
00:20:13,380 --> 00:20:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

336
00:20:15,100 --> 00:20:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm thinking about maybe 
starting running or s-something.</font>

337
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Will you teach me good form and stuff—</font>

338
00:20:22,020 --> 00:20:26,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got you! Let's train to run the 
100-meter in under 12 seconds together!</font>

339
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}N-Nukumizu!</font>

340
00:20:28,090 --> 00:20:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You owe me one! W-Wait up...</font>

341
00:20:32,890 --> 00:20:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinda weird, isn't it?</font>

342
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I never really crossed paths 
with you or Komari-chan before.</font>

343
00:20:41,390 --> 00:20:46,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I didn't really know what the lit club 
did until we went camping together.</font>

344
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when I tried writing, I really enjoyed it.</font>

345
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I liked the books 
Komari-chan recommended.</font>

346
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think books are great.</font>

347
00:21:05,890 --> 00:21:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter?</font>

348
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yanami-san, we need to talk.</font>

349
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? We do?</font>

350
00:21:12,530 --> 00:21:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. About something really important.</font>

351
00:21:19,050 --> 00:21:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now wait just a second!</font>

352
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nukumizu-kun, you should probably think 
this through carefully one more time.</font>

353
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've thought about it enough. 
If I don't say it right now, I know I'll regret it.</font>

354
00:21:31,770 --> 00:21:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, okay.</font>

355
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll just listen, then.</font>

356
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:44,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yanami-san, will you...</font>

357
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes?</font>

358
00:21:49,490 --> 00:21:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...please become friends with me?</font>

359
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry! I think of you as a friend!</font>

360
00:21:56,770 --> 00:21:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Become friends?</font>

361
00:21:58,310 --> 00:21:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

362
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all you meant?</font>

363
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold on a sec.</font>

364
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't even ask you out and
 you already turned me down?!</font>

365
00:22:11,950 --> 00:22:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah, I guess you could say I did.</font>

366
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome to the land of the dumped.</font>

367
00:22:18,900 --> 00:22:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't dumped! I didn't ask you out!</font>

368
00:22:21,510 --> 00:22:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I was going to ask you out, first we'd 
have to be friends for two or three years,</font>

369
00:22:25,360 --> 00:22:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then once we'd confirmed our feelings 
for each other, we could, um...</font>

370
00:22:28,410 --> 00:22:32,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean you're going to propose 
to me in three years, Nukumizu-kun?</font>

371
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I save you the trouble and say "no" now?</font>

372
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm not! I mean, that's different!</font>

373
00:22:36,860 --> 00:22:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just friends anyway, aren't we?</font>

374
00:22:39,600 --> 00:22:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Are we?</font>

375
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:44,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What else would we be?</font>

376
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I'm talking about, Nukumizu-kun.</font>

377
00:22:49,430 --> 00:22:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is what you're 
talking about, Yanami-san?</font>

378
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Yanami-san.</font>

379
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're very welcome.</font>

380
00:23:01,810 --> 00:23:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to befriend you, fellow dumpee.</font>

381
00:23:14,610 --> 00:23:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still haven't been dumped, though.</font>

382
